13	//!   indices. Exact index equality across CPU and MLX is NOT
14	//!   asserted -- losses close within fp32 tolerance can
15	//!   reorder if two entries race at the tolerance boundary.
16	//! - Ensemble logits share the same shape as a single
17	//!   variant's forward output.
